OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,FA campaign group, 'Save International
OL,8,FHouse', has criticised Lambeth Council
OL,9,Ffor approving a redevelopment project
OL,10,Fwhich will see over 100 not-for-profit
OL,11,Forganisations, community initiatives,
OL,12,Fand charities evicted.
OL,14,FYesterday, Lambeth Council approved
OL,15,Fthe plan to develop the site stating
OL,16,Fthat it would be used for affordable,
OL,17,Fas well as private, housing.
OL,19,FElena Lo Presdi is the founder and
OL,20,Fdirector of a not-for-profit group,
OL,21,FCraft Forward.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,FShe is currently a tenant at
OL,8,FInternational House and is worried
OL,9,Fabout the future.
OL,11,FShe said:" The issue is that over 100
OL,12,Forganisations will not have a HQ and
OL,13,Fwon't be able to continue providing
OL,14,Fthe services that we do in Brixton for
OL,15,Feverybody, the whole of the local
OL,16,Fcommunity.
OL,18,F"We run free knitting and crochet
OL,19,Fworkshops. We won't be able to run
OL,20,Fthose. "
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,FElena continued: "There's also so many
OL,8,Fmore organisations that have so many
OL,9,Fdifferent provisions and people will
OL,10,Fnot be able to access any of those.
OL,12,F"If you've got a kid that is doing
OL,13,Ffree football classes, they won't be
OL,14,Fable to do that.
OL,16,F"If you've ever experienced food
OL,17,Finsecurity, Lambeth Larder is in here,
OL,18,Fand they have a directory of all soup
OL,19,Fkitchens and you won't be able to
OL,20,Faccess that anymore.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,F"If you're trying to learn English.
OL,8,FThere's an organisation that does that.
OL,10,F"There's just so many of us and
OL,11,Feverybody here has probably interacted
OL,12,Fwith our organisations at some point,
OL,13,Fso none of this will be able to happen
OL,14,Fanymore, at least not locally."
OL,16,FElena told ITV News London that the
OL,17,Fbiggest issue is that there are no
OL,18,Fother affordable workspaces in Lambeth:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,F"The only option we were sent by
OL,8,FLambeth as an alternative are spaces
OL,9,Fthat can be over #40,000 a year.
OL,11,F"The majority of the organizations
OL,12,Fhere have a turnover of under #10,000.
OL,14,F"So how can they afford something like
OL,15,Fthat?
OL,17,F"There is no other choice except going
OL,18,Faway from Lambeth which would mean
OL,19,Flosing our entire community."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
