FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,FElena isn't the only tenant who is
OL,8,Fworried about what will happen if they
OL,9,Fare evicted.
OL,11,FCarly Whyborn is the Chief Operating
OL,12,FOfficer at Refugees at Home she fears
OL,13,Fthe charity will be left without a
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,FShe said: "I think it would be really
OL,17,Fhard for us because of, as I say, this
OL,18,Fsense of community that we have.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,F"It's made our charity stronger. It's
OL,8,Fmade our charity better simply by
OL,9,Ffeeling like we're at home here.
OL,11,F"We're with people that know what we
OL,12,Fdo. They love what we do and we love
OL,13,Fwhat they do as well.
OL,15,F"So I don't know what we would do if
OL,16,Fwe didn't have International House."
OL,18,FThe charity connects people with a
OL,19,Fspare room in their home to refugees
OL,20,Fand people seeking asylum, in need of
OL,21,Fsomewhere to stay.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
