PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,FWatch below: The charity is worried
OL,8,Fabout losing the community it has at
OL,9,FInternational House.
OL,11,FShe said: "I think us being a stable
OL,12,Fcharity, someone that a refugee who
OL,13,Fhas been through so much already can
OL,15,Fgenuinely trust, that they know we're
OL,16,Fgoing to be here to support them.
OL,18,F"That stability of having a base,
OL,19,Fhaving a home, is so vital.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
