FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,F"I think it might change how people
OL,8,Ffeel about us if we're not in a really
OL,9,Fstable environment."
OL,11,FInternational House was sold to London
OL,12,FSquare, a property development company
OL,13,Fowned by Aldar Properties- which is in
OL,14,Fturn part owned by the Abu Dhabi
OL,15,Fsovereign wealth fund, Mubadala
OL,16,FInvestment Company.
OL,18,FLambeth Council say the plans will
OL,19,Fprovide 288 new homes, and 40% of
OL,20,Fthese will be affordable housing.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
