PN,40410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,FThey say current tenants will be able
OL,8,Fto access ongoing support and a
OL,9,Fpackage of relocation support ahead of
OL,10,Fthe planned end of the project.
OL,12,FInternational House used to be a
OL,13,FLambeth Council office, but was
OL,14,Fvacated in 2018 to save money, it has
OL,15,Fsince been used as a temporary
OL,16,Fworkspace while master planning
OL,17,Fprogressed.
OL,19,FCouncillor Danny Adilypour, Lambeth's
OL,20,FDeputy Leader (Housing, Investment and
OL,21,FNew Homes), said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/13
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,F"I welcome planning permission being
OL,8,Fgranted for this important Brixton
OL,9,Ftown centre scheme that has been
OL,10,Fdesigned to meet the needs of
OL,11,Fresidents and businesses.
OL,13,F"In the face of the housing crisis,
OL,14,Fwhich is having a huge effect in
OL,15,FLambeth, and across London, we are
OL,16,Fdetermined to use council owned land
OL,17,Fto build as many new homes as possible
OL,18,Ffor everyone.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
