OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1774703465
OL,3,COver 100 charities and community
OL,4,Cgroups will be evicted from
OL,5,CInternational House
OL,7,F"The temporary schemes on these two
OL,8,Fsites have served the community well
OL,9,Fand brought activity to these spaces
OL,10,Fwhilst these plans progressed, but
OL,11,Fit's now time to secure a permanent
OL,12,Ffuture for these sites.
OL,14,F"This project is focused on town
OL,15,Fcentre improvements and really meeting
OL,16,FBrixton's needs, especially when it
OL,17,Fcomes to new affordable workspace and
OL,18,Fnew homes."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@KO]
